Package com.nalinstudios.iscan.graphics Description

This package consists of the classes which are involved in the manipulation and editing of the images. The classes in this package are:
  1. ImageProcessor : A class that will be used to perform operations with the images like finding corners, cropping, etc.
  2. ImgHelper : A helper class that contains internal functions while processing images using the ImageProcessor Class.
Author:
Nalin Angrish.
